OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright this morning,
OL,6,Fwith periods of hazy sunshine. This
OL,7,Fafternoon cloud thickens and outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain arrive from the west late
OL,9,Fafternoon to early evening. Becoming
OL,10,Fwarm for many places, away from
OL,11,Fcooling coastal onshore breezes.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely cloudy with outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain, these possibly heavy at
OL,15,Ftimes, clearing east. Generally cloudy
OL,16,Fconditions and a few showers will
OL,17,Ffollow, with the showers most likely
OL,18,Facross the Pennines.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
