OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fisolated mainly light showers, these
OL,7,Fmost likely across the Pennines early
OL,8,Fin the day. Temperatures will be
OL,9,Fnoticeably lower than previous days.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,12,Fdry start then outbreaks of rain soon
OL,13,Fspread east. Tuesday sunshine and
OL,14,Fshowers, some heavy with perhaps hail
OL,15,Fand thunder. Wednesday mainly dry and
OL,16,Ffine before rain arrives later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
